This video shows you how to find vulnerabilities in WordPress, enumerate WP users and how to brute force passwords using WPScan in Kali Linux. WPScan is a must have tool for any WordPress web developer to scan for vulnerabilities and solve issues before they get exploited.

Check out the Full article here: http://www.hackingtutorials.org/web-application-hacking/hack-a-wordpress-website-with-wpscan/

